             was indicted for <rs id="t17830115-15-off99" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830115-15-off99" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830115-15-off99" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17830115-15-cd100" type="crimeDate">12th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830115-15-off99 t17830115-15-cd100"></join> last, eight yards and an half of lawn, value 15 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830115-15-victim199" type="victimName">
